
Save that file as `README.md` in your project root.

---

### 2. Add a LICENSE file

- Go to [choosealicense.com](https://choosealicense.com/licenses/mit/) and copy the MIT License text (recommended for open-source and simplicity).
- Create a file called `LICENSE` in your project root.
- Paste the MIT license text, then replace `[year]` with current year and `[fullname]` with your name or username.

Example:

```text
MIT License

Copyright (c) 2025 Marksman247

Permission is hereby granted, free of charge, to any person obtaining a copy
...
